$OpenBSD: patch-src_tools_Makefile_in,v 1.1 2011/11/24 09:29:55 ajacoutot Exp $

Reorder LDFLAGS (prefer -L.libs over /usr/local/lib) so that bacula can
be rebuilt while already installed.

